cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with video feature learning and temporal modeling, which are closely related to computer vision and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also involves multimedia analysis and natural language processing, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) respectively. Finally, the paper uses unsupervised learning techniques, which could also be relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
